-kills-3-pak-soldiers-jk-police-neutralise-jaish-terrorist-in-pulwama/articleshow/62248391.cms] 23 killed (2017),[https://www.firstpost.com/india/jammu-and-kashmir-indian-army-jawan-killed-after-pakistan-violates-ceasefire-along-loc-in-rajouri-sector-4301437.html] 25 killed (2018),[https://www.deccanherald.com/national/officer-among-4-bsf-personnel-killed-pak-rangers-firing-along-ib-samba-674662.html][https://www.telegraphindia.com/india/soldier-killed-in-pakistan-shelling-across-loc-in-rajouti-dgtl-238166] total of 61 soldiers reported killed</ref><ref>25 killed (2016\u201317),[http://indianexpress.com/article/india/25-civilians-killed-163-injured-due-to-pak-shelling-in-2016-2017-jk-govt-5037860/] 26 killed (2018),[https://www.deccanherald.com/national/officer-among-4-bsf-personnel-killed-pak-rangers-firing-along-ib-samba-674662.html] total of 51 civilians reported killed</ref>\n\n86\u201390 soldiers killed <small>(Pakistani claim)</small><ref>40\u201344 killed (29 Sep.\u201317 Nov. 2016),[https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/army-rejects-pakistans-claim-of-killing-11-indian-soldiers-at-line-of-control-1626430] 6 killed (21 Nov. 2016),[https://www.dawn.com/news/1297732/] 7 killed (24 Nov. 2016),[https://www.dawn.com/news/1298279/10-civilians-three-soldiers-killed-in-indian-shelling] 5 killed (3 June 2017),[https://nation.com.pk/03-Jun-2017/five-indian-soldiers-killed-as-pakistani-troops-respond-to-firing-along-loc-ispr] 4 killed (10 July 2017),[https://www.dawn.com/news/1344221] 5 killed (19 July 2017),[https://tribune.com.pk/story/1461749/pak-army-kills-5-indian-soldiers-destroys-posts-response-ceasefire-violations/] 3 killed (21 July 2017),[https://www.samaa.tv/pakistan/2017/07/3-indian-soldiers-killed-as-pakistan-responds-to-unprovoked-shelling/] 3 killed (4 Oct. 2017),[https://www.thenews.com.pk/latest/234473-Two-children-martyred-as-Indian-forces-target-civilians-in-cross-border-firing] 7 killed (23 Nov. 2017),[https://www.apnews.com/842ae01904f348d4b4c2c80750447e6